    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="博客错误合集：（持续更新……）"><a href="#博客错误合集：（持续更新……）" class="headerlink" title="博客错误合集：（持续更新……）"></a>博客错误合集：（持续更新……）</h1><h2 id="npm命令遇到6-vulnerabilities-2-low-1-high-3-critical"><a href="#npm命令遇到6-vulnerabilities-2-low-1-high-3-critical" class="headerlink" title="npm命令遇到6 vulnerabilities (2 low, 1 high, 3 critical)"></a>npm命令遇到6 vulnerabilities (2 low, 1 high, 3 critical)</h2><p>按照命令行提示输入<code>npm audit</code></p><p>npm audit report如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">markdown  *</span><br><span class="line">Regular Expression Denial of Service in markdown - https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-wx77-rp39-c6vg</span><br><span class="line">fix available via `npm audit fix --force`</span><br><span class="line">Will install hexo-renderer-swig@1.1.0, which is a breaking change</span><br><span class="line">node_modules/markdown</span><br><span class="line">  swig-extras  *</span><br><span class="line">  Depends on vulnerable versions of markdown</span><br><span class="line">  node_modules/swig-extras</span><br><span class="line">    hexo-renderer-swig  *</span><br><span class="line">    Depends on vulnerable versions of swig-extras</span><br><span class="line">    Depends on vulnerable versions of swig-templates</span><br><span class="line">    node_modules/hexo-renderer-swig</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">minimist  &lt;=0.2.3</span><br><span class="line">Severity: critical</span><br><span class="line">Prototype Pollution in minimist - https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-vh95-rmgr-6w4m</span><br><span class="line">Prototype Pollution in minimist - https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-xvch-5gv4-984h</span><br><span class="line">fix available via `npm audit fix --force`</span><br><span class="line">Will install hexo-renderer-swig@1.1.0, which is a breaking change</span><br><span class="line">node_modules/optimist/node_modules/minimist</span><br><span class="line">  optimist  &gt;=0.6.0</span><br><span class="line">  Depends on vulnerable versions of minimist</span><br><span class="line">  node_modules/optimist</span><br><span class="line">    swig-templates  *</span><br><span class="line">    Depends on vulnerable versions of optimist</span><br><span class="line">    node_modules/swig-templates</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">6 vulnerabilities (2 low, 1 high, 3 critical)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">To address all issues (including breaking changes), run:</span><br><span class="line">  npm audit fix --force</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按照命令行提示继续输入<code>npm audit fix --force</code>没有用，在仔细查看错误报告后，发现 <code>hexo-renderer-swig</code>插件出现了问题。解决方法如下：</p><ul><li>打开项目的 <code>package.json</code> 文件。</li><li>将 <code>&quot;hexo-renderer-swig&quot;</code> 替换为 <code>&quot;hexo-renderer-nunjucks&quot;</code></li><li>执行 <code>npm audit fix --force</code></li></ul><p>详情见：<a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-renderer-swig">hexojs&#x2F;hexo-renderer-swig: Swig renderer for Hexo (github.com)</a></p><h2 id="更换Wikitten主题遇到的错误"><a href="#更换Wikitten主题遇到的错误" class="headerlink" title="更换Wikitten主题遇到的错误"></a>更换Wikitten主题遇到的错误</h2><p>换主题：<a href="https://github.com/zthxxx/hexo-theme-Wikitten/blob/master/README_zh-CN.md">hexo-theme-Wikitten&#x2F;README_zh-CN.md at master · zthxxx&#x2F;hexo-theme-Wikitten (github.com)</a></p><p>安装插件未成功，查询后改为使用(–&gt;)以下插件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo-autonofollow    // 打开非本站链接时自动开启新标签页 --&gt; npm i hexo-filter-nofollow --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo-directory-category // 根据文章文件目录自动为文章添加分类 --&gt; npm install --save hexo-directory-category</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-feed    // 生成 RSS 源 --&gt; npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-json-content// 生成全站文章 json 内容，用于全文搜索 --&gt; npm i -S hexo-generator-json-content</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-sitemap// 生成全站站点地图 sitemap --&gt; npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中<em><strong>最</strong>抽象的一个错误</em>：</p><p>查看教程中有以下命令，认识错误在theme下新建了source和scaffolds两个文件夹……一直配置错误……</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp -rf themes/Wikitten/_source/* source/ </span><br><span class="line">cp -rf themes/Wikitten/_scaffolds/* scaffolds/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>newbing的解释：这些指令是用于在Linux或Mac系统中复制文件或文件夹的。cp是复制的意思，-r是递归的意思，-f是强制覆盖的意思。themes&#x2F;Wikitten&#x2F;_source&#x2F;*和themes&#x2F;Wikitten&#x2F;_scaffolds&#x2F;*是源文件夹，source&#x2F;和scaffolds&#x2F;是目标文件夹。这些指令的作用是将Wikitten主题的源文件和脚手架文件复制到Hexo站点的相应文件夹中</p><h2 id="Hexo更新后无法上传至github"><a href="#Hexo更新后无法上传至github" class="headerlink" title="Hexo更新后无法上传至github"></a>Hexo更新后无法上传至github</h2><p>修改_config.yml中的#url部分如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># URL</span><br><span class="line">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as &#x27;http://yoursite.com/child&#x27; and root as &#x27;/child/&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">url: https://agingse.github.io/</span><br><span class="line">root: /</span><br><span class="line">permalink: wiki/:title/</span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参照：<a href="https://chaflee.github.io/charlesleeblog/2022/12/30/Hexo%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Github%E7%A9%BA%E7%99%BD%E9%A1%B5%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/">Hexo部署Github空白页问题 (chaflee.github.io)</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
